    "asOf": "2020-10-30",
    "date": "2020-12-08T13:50:08Z",
    "text": "This bill extends the statute of limitations for civil and criminal violations of federal campaign finance laws.\n\nSpecifically, it extends the statute of limitations for civil violations from 5 years to 15 years, and for criminal violations from 5 years to 10 years."
